Boring. Predictable and tired storyline that has gotten old with these animated movies. Dumb. The children in the group thought it was ok nothing special. Even with all of the sexual connotations and symbolism, each adult in the group was falling asleep 10 minutes in.
A bland, uninspired, cringe-worthy movie, this is a movie that you might want your kids to avoid.
This movie was moving. It showed me that you don't have to be normal to fit in, and much like myself, who isn't normal in many ways, i it was great. Perfect.

Don't even watch this movie ironically. Seriously, just don't waste your time or money. It's not "so bad it's good" and it's not even funny or enjoyable in an ironic way. It's just straight up bad with zero enjoyable scenes. It's not even a good movie to watch just to make fun of it; you'll only end up feeling like you're watching paint dry in the movie theater. It's just not worth it.
